## Overview

This document provides ready-to-use trust indicators, security badges, and verifiable claims for A-B/AI's security posture. Each indicator includes evidence and verification methods.

## Trust Badges & Implementation

### üîí PCI DSS Compliant

**Badge HTML**:
```html
<div class="trust-badge pci-dss">
  <img src="/badges/pci-dss-compliant.svg" alt="PCI DSS Compliant">
  <span class="badge-text">PCI DSS Compliant</span>
  <a href="/security/pci-compliance" class="verify-link">Verify</a>
</div>
```

**Claim**: "PCI DSS Compliant Payment Processing"

**Evidence**:
- SAQ-A eligible through Stripe integration
- No direct card data handling
- Webhook signature validation implemented
- Regular security testing

**Verification Page Content**:
```markdown
# PCI DSS Compliance Verification

A-B/AI maintains PCI DSS compliance through:
- Stripe (PCI Level 1) handles all card processing
- No credit card data stored or transmitted through our systems
- Secure webhook validation prevents payment fraud
- Annual self-assessment questionnaire (SAQ-A) completion

Last Assessment: [Date]
Next Assessment: [Annual]
Status: COMPLIANT
```

